{"tid":2204488,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"濫捕過千人 家長被送「再教育營」  內蒙硬推漢教逼死九人","createTime":"2020-09-16T05:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T06:14:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"207b039a515cd58a0bae6bbadbac29fd25821d9d","tid":2204488,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200916/JTB5JVOOPZG4FPSPCAGEOB6SHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200916%2FJTB5JVOOPZG4FPSPCAGEOB6SHQ%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvaFdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=2f4904e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200916%2FJTB5JVOOPZG4FPSPCAGEOB6SHQ%2F&h=4d64a8d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200916/JTB5JVOOPZG4FPSPCAGEOB6SHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n濫捕過千人 家長被送「再教育營」 <br />\n內蒙硬推漢教逼死九人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/L7Xu2qwIWN91vCxHTaPSKg-baK8=/2996x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NMGLWZGIR5BGHB7SUKBGOK3OSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FL7Xu2qwIWN91vCxHTaPSKg-baK8%3D%2F2996x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNMGLWZGIR5BGHB7SUKBGOK3OSM.jpg&h=02bee101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內蒙當局以各手段威逼利誘學生返學，圖為警察在通遼蒙古族中學外執勤。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中共在內蒙強推漢語教學，激起蒙古族人激烈抵抗。開學至今兩周，內蒙政府強推「推漢廢蒙」之心不死，除了大肆拘捕過千人，又以不同的手段去脅逼蒙古人就範，包括免職、罰款，更要求反抗漢語教學的蒙古人上「法制教育培訓班」，旅日的蒙古族學者忽必斯質疑這有如新疆的「再教育營」。據南蒙古人權信息中心統計，截至前日，已有至少九人因當局強推漢語教學而被逼死。<br />\n<br />\n南蒙古人權信息中心統計，截至前日，內蒙為了推行教改，當局已經逼死九人，包括日前跳樓身亡的一名校長。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地方官為領功緝捕家長<br />\n<br />\n當局為了要讓內蒙小孩回校，可說是無所不用其極。一份下款為「阿巴嘎旗國家通用教材相關工作指揮部」的文件要求基層官員三天內必須送孩子到校，否則會被問責，拒絕送孩子上學的幹部父母會被免去職位，牧民則可能被拒在銀行貸款，或得不到低收入保障。當地政府甚至發出文件硬性規定前日起各學校要有一定的入學率，當中明確指出前日下午5時前到校率要達70%、昨日要達90%、今日就要全員到校。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙各地的官方昨日也急着出來領功，多地的民族學校均稱截至前日早上10時，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n旅日的蒙古族學者忽必斯對本報指出，官方公佈的數字並不可信，在牧區很多小孩都不回校，當局甚至派出特警到牧區抓父母，然後把小孩帶到學校。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙多地的人民法院、人民檢察院、公安局、教育局及司法局五大機關也發出聯合。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙於上月下旬要求新學年加強推行漢語教學，要求幾科原本由蒙古語言教授的科目。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UKOQtXRzXuLsNwjmNr4lFcgYYAs=/2454x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P5R2OEHA6ZHO7DZ7YUZKPVMVNI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUKOQtXRzXuLsNwjmNr4lFcgYYAs%3D%2F2454x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP5R2OEHA6ZHO7DZ7YUZKPVMVNI.jpg&h=53b0514e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有內蒙學生被迫返校，無助下忍不住落淚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EtWMwHoGtVfuqqweIQQSG_vdN_0=/2490x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NJ3T7EB3SNBNROQREQQFNPVQPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEtWMwHoGtVfuqqweIQQSG_vdN_0%3D%2F2490x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNJ3T7EB3SNBNROQREQQFNPVQPY.jpg&h=da0d2750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■當局派幹部騷擾家長，強迫他們送子女返學。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EgSRWmi8ZviNbFubwhQiySovi9Q=/1323x1130/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6637B6QGKBGOPH5TI6SH7OV7VU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEgSRWmi8ZviNbFubwhQiySovi9Q%3D%2F1323x1130%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6637B6QGKBGOPH5TI6SH7OV7VU.gif&h=eac35d60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"452afa6996d3d57a390499fb30c984e7e7b531e0","tid":2204488,"uid":47492,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T05:58: